Text.CultureInvariantString:
WELL WHAT A GREAT LOAD 
OF GOOD ALL THE GUARD'S 
TRAINING HAD DONE

A STELLAR JOB 
ALL ROUND 
STOPPING THE 
WRETCHED RODENT 
FROM GETTING PAST 
AND GRANTING 
ACCESS TO HIS 
CHUMS

THE TROOPS WOULD 
SURELY BE COMMENDING 
EACH OTHER FOR THEIR 
FLAWLESS PERFORMANCE

FROM THE BOTTOM 
OF THE PIT INTO 
WHICH THEY WOULD 
SOON BE BANISHED.
